\c 15
\s Ndiani angagara
\s mutende raJehovha?
\p
\v 151 Jehovha, ndianiko
\s angatsaukira mutende renyu? Ndianiko angagara pagomo renyu dzvene?
\p
\v 2 Uyo, anofamba asina mhosva, anoita zvakarurama,
\s Anotaura zvokwadi mumwoyo make.
\p
\v 3 Iye asina makuhwa parurimi rwake, Asingaitiri shamwari yake zvakaipa, Asingatuki waagere naye.
\p
\v 4 Munhu akashata anozvidzwa naye; Asi anokudza vanotya Jehovha. Iye anoti kana achinge apika, haangazoshanduri shoko rake,
\s kunyange zvikava zvakaipa kwaari.
\p
\v 5 Iye asingarevi mhindu pamari yake, Kana kugamuchira chipo pamusoro pausina mhosva.
\s Munhu anoita zvinhu izvozvi
\s haangatongozonunguswi.
